choices.text:
when I was 6, my sister was half my age. Now I am 80. How old is my sister now?
If you were 6 when your sister was half your age and now you are 80, then at that time your sister would have been 3 (since she was half of your age). So, if your sister was 3 years old when you were 6, then now, when you are 80, your sister is 74.
